null, "text": "Dave如果gcd真的这么身体力行就好了", "timestamp": 1630761191, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2434790, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 463806, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "你是南疆的吗", "timestamp": 1630761516, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2434888, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 463806, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "你是新疆人吗", "timestamp": 1630762719, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2434948, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 463806, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "（弱弱问一句）最被歧视的不是汉族吗", "timestamp": 1630763290, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2434962, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 463806, "reply_to": 2434888, "tag": null, "text": "Re Francis，Re Eve: 不是 ", "timestamp": 1630763384, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2435025, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 463806, "reply_to": 2434962, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 有人歧视新疆的民族么", "timestamp": 1630763986, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2435173, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 463806, "reply_to": 2435025, "tag": null, "text": "Re Francis: 你没听说过吗？新疆棉花", "timestamp": 1630765317, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2435213, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 463806, "reply_to": 2435173, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: pinky要来叻", "timestamp": 1630765691, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2435267, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 463806, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "新疆怎么了", "timestamp": 1630766264, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2435427, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 463806, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "新疆棉花是种族歧视吗？/是强迫劳动吗？", "timestamp": 1630767464